EU Aims to Speed Bank Capital Increases, French Official Says

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-10-13T10:03:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/eu-aims-to-speed-bank-capital-increases-french-official-says.html
European finance ministers are
considering setting a new timetable for banks to strengthen
their balance sheets under the Basel III framework, a French
official said. Asked if a 9 percent tier-1 capital ratio would
be acceptable, the official said “yes.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
